data.name: اکسنت مدیا
data.description: Founded in 2010, Axent Media is a small web design & development agency based in Tbilisi, Georgia. Over the last few years we’ve made a reputation for building websites that look great and are easy-to-use. Our approach is both intelligent and down to earth. A love for the web, great design and the latest technologies means your project is more than just a job. We specialize in creating the best possible website that can fit into your budget.
